ft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-layout-id&quot;:&quot;17&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 17px; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(0,0,0,0.9); margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 2.0&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-start&quot;:&quot;1979&quot;,&quot;data-end&quot;:&quot;2074&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;system-ui\\&quot;, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">感兴趣的朋友可以关注AINLP公众号回复'kimiatt</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-layout-id&quot;:&quot;17&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 17px; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(0,0,0,0.9); margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 2.0&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-start&quot;:&quot;1979&quot;,&quot;data-end&quot;:&quot;2074&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;system-ui\\&quot;, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">'获取该技术报告英中对照版pdf全文</span></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文深入解读了 Kimi (月之暗面) 提出的 Attention Residuals 架构，该方案通过在深度维度引入注意力机制取代传统残差连接的固定累加，实现了跨层信息的按需检索与高效聚合。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文深入解读了 Kimi (月之暗面) 提出的 Attention Residuals 架构，该方案通过在深度维度引入注意力机制取代传统残差连接的固定累加，实现了跨层信息的按需检索与高效聚合。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了 Kimi 团队针对 Transformer 核心组件——残差连接的创新改进。传统残差连接采用固定累加方式，导致深层网络难以定向找回被压缩的历史信息。新提出的 Attention Residuals (AttnRes) 允许每一层通过注意力机制在深度维度上自主选择和检索历史层表示。为了平衡性能与工程可行性，作者进一步提出了 Block AttnRes，将复杂度降至可部署范围。实验证明，该方法在不同规模下均能优化 Scaling Law 曲线，并有效缓解 PreNorm 稀释问题，使梯度分布更均衡，为大模型架构的深度扩展提供了新的设计思路。",
